news.h: Basile carries Wright State past Youngstown State 84-71
news.a: DAYTON, Ohio (AP) — Grant Basile had 29 points and Tanner Holden added 27 points as Wright State topped Youngstown State 84-71 on Thursday night.

news.h: Youngstown State survives scare from IUPUI to remain in hunt for top-four seed
news.a: The Youngstown State men’s basketball team grabbed their eighth win in their last nine games, topping IUPUI 74-61

news.h: Akuchie scores 21 to lift Youngstown St. over IUPUI 74-61
news.a: YOUNGSTOWN, Ohio (AP) — Michael Akuchie had 21 points and 13 rebounds as Youngstown State defeated IUPUI 74-61 on Saturday.

news.h: Cohill scores 31 to carry Youngstown St. over UIC 88-79
news.a: YOUNGSTOWN, Ohio (AP) — Dwayne Cohill had a career-high 31 points as Youngstown State beat Illinois-Chicago 88-79 on Thursday night.

news.h: Spear scores 27 as Robert Morris tops Youngstown State 73-68
news.a: YOUNGSTOWN, Ohio (AP) — Kahliel Spear scored 27 points to lead four in double figures and Robert Morris defeated Youngstown State 73-68 on Sunday.
